{"tid":1243173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係急症室返工，今日講下急症室求診既程序。","createTime":"2019-06-19T10:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T13:26:29.000Z","uid":9347,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a092a51a20779fc62d41b512ad64d8c3852ad2a7","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YaMPZCi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYaMPZCi.png&h=22e47229&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先附上employment letter 一張<br />\n<br />\n相信好多人冇乜事都唔會去急症睇醫生，今日就講下由入嚟開始，到底會發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論你係坐白車定walk-in 入嚟，第一站要先去或者請同你陪診嗰個去入院登記處admission office 做登記。Admission office 會幫你開case 每個case 都會有自己既編號，叫AE number 。所有工作人員都可以用你個AE number 嚟睇返你嗰次係急症求診既記錄。同一時間，佢地會幫你開一張求診記錄卡(AE卡)。有呢兩樣嘢你就可以去分流站等分流。<br />\n<br />\n分流站(Triage station) 顧名思義就係分流既地方。分流站既護士同職工會幫你初部檢查維生指素，例如體溫，血壓之類。之後佢地會因應病人既情況分成5個category <br />\n<br />\nCat 1 危殆 ：因嚴重事件或意外引致有生命危險，主要維生指標（如脈搏、呼吸、血壓等）極不穩定，必須立即施行搶救<br />\nCat 2 危急 ：主要維生指標處於邊緣情況，可能有生命危險，須立即治理及密切監察病情。<br />\nCat 3 緊急 ：主要維生指標較為穩定，但情況嚴重須盡早治理。<br />\nCat 4 次緊急 ：情況較輕微但需要治理，可以等候一段時間而不致出現病情惡化。<br />\nCat 5 非緊急 ：屬於非急症，可以考慮使用其他醫療服務，如公立普通科門診，或私人家庭醫生。<br />\n<br />\n注意返，如果touchwood你現場或者白車上面情況好懷，基本上會skip 曬上面嗰part 直入急救室(R房)"},{"pid":"ccf83ae6110718c585281f94747490f71a63045a","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:46:04.000Z","msg":"抖一抖再打"},{"pid":"2194de982b1b6c30a75b91d9746e77d0640543ca","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:49:26.000Z","msg":"上面打漏，分流站都會記錄底你求醫既原因同病情。"},{"pid":"04f7e34f133a2cbe9d2c3cb739d7f2552abc42c2","tid":1243173,"uid":245030,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:49:55.000Z","msg":"巴打係護士？"},{"pid":"6d4715d83af950f619c56b76739a17bde0b88858","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"過分流之後就會等見醫生。因應你既分流等級，你既等待時間都會唔同。見咗醫生之後，醫生就會按病情需要而決定做咩檢查，抽血，x光，CT等。喺一啲特殊情況下，急性室醫生亦都會請求其他專科醫生做consultations ，常見例如眼科，耳鼻喉科，情神科。<br />\n<br />\n之後病人就會推返去大堂/RAT區等做檢查。以QEH 為例X光報告一般等候時間係個半鐘，而血報告就三個鐘。出咗報告之後醫生睇定就會決定個病人係可以出院(Discharge)定係要留醫觀察(Admit)"},{"pid":"423563b39becaf4b982b2ec6daa01152814b5646","tid":1243173,"uid":41389,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:05:50.000Z","msg":"絲打 你唔遮埋個date會唔會比HA trace到?"},{"pid":"de9522dccaedfcbbca089699fc79a806893036c2","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:16:07.000Z","msg":"先講入院<br />\n<br />\n醫生決定病人要入院，醫生會因應唔同科目分病人上病房，然後叫陪診去入院登記處打排版入院。排版係一個紙皮套咁既嘢，而原先既AE number 都會改做HN number。入面會有病人既AE卡副本，所有已經出咗既Report 等等，方便上到去病房啲同事可以等一時間知到病情。<br />\n<br />\n如果病房上面冇空床既話，病人就會入Observation room 等床。要等幾耐真係冇人知，我曾經見過有個老人家等骨科床等咗三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca286ac4acf8e13c7dbc3358bc2ff3586ae81aea","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"423563b39becaf4b982b2ec6daa01152814b5646","tid":1243173,"uid":41389,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:05:50.000Z","msg":"絲打 你唔遮埋個date會唔會比HA trace到?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:16:36.000Z","msg":"一早揚咗唔怕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b68ebec5fcfcbbbcffd8dcf9c50dd55ee51b69","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:29:13.000Z","msg":"出院(Discharged)<br />\n<br />\nDischarge 係指醫生俾病人出院。醫生睇過啲report 覺得冇乜大礙就會俾病人出院，得罪講句，見你冇乜事就快啲俾你走，空個位出嚟幫其他新嚟既病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時啲report 未出，病人心急想走，醫生都會批。Report 冇事未冇事，但係如果出咗事就會叫當值既護士長NOIC打電話叫你返嚟，所以<br />\n醫院電話一定要聽！<br />\n醫院電話一定要聽！<br />\n醫院電話一定要聽！<br />\n<br />\n一般情況下，醫生俾你出院，拎藥紙同出院文件( Discharged summary )，找數，你就可以走。"},{"pid":"86ee9630b17b404ba4bba6e52c38ae62c8d710e9","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:51:18.000Z","msg":"講完一般情況，依家講埋非常情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n通常特殊出院情況有 Disappeared DAMA 同 DBA。<br />\n<br />\nDisappeared 係指病人係冇通知醫院就自己走咗去，醫生會因應病人情況而決定需唔需要報警。例如病人精神情況不穩，老人痴呆，自殺傾向等 (通常呢種病人會俾我地鎖係一間單人房同著安全背心)。另外係個病人本身有高度傳染性疾病例如肺結核。所以咁大個人如果唔等的話都同我地同事講聲唔好要我地擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外就係DAMA Discharged Against Medical Advice (好似係) 。意思係醫生要你入院/留低但係你決定要走。姐係一般所謂既簽紙出院。你決定簽紙出院之後醫生會俾份form 你簽，內容係你自願承擔所有唔聽醫生講既後果。如果擔心既都係乖乖地等下啦，條命係自己，無謂慳嗰少少時間。<br />\n<br />\nDBA Death Before Arrival 。姐係送醫途中身亡，嚟到醫生都會再check 下vital signs 然後先再call certified death 。"},{"pid":"7e8813825b8bf5462a969600067c7b393e9ed6c7","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:53:55.000Z","msg":"大致上係咁多，有漏諗到再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家身體健康唔洗嚟探我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n了解多啲成個程序，多一個保障，20/21 加油"},{"pid":"33ba21585353fee0141337194dbf9ee8c1202557","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"04f7e34f133a2cbe9d2c3cb739d7f2552abc42c2","tid":1243173,"uid":245030,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:49:55.000Z","msg":"巴打係護士？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fdbcd206b9e1c1ba8c05351befe701b476f73f0","tid":1243173,"uid":178682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:55:12.000Z","msg":"唔關事但想問一問<br />\n鯁骨去急症算唔算濫用？"},{"pid":"86f2370569785225c8adc09bffd6d2c0a3892978","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7fdbcd206b9e1c1ba8c05351befe701b476f73f0","tid":1243173,"uid":178682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:55:12.000Z","msg":"唔關事但想問一問<br />\n鯁骨去急症算唔算濫用？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:58:31.000Z","msg":"都唔算既，因為一般診所應該處理唔到鯁骨。再者如果係小朋友或者老人家鯁其實都幾危險。"},{"pid":"c4e262d0498dd80711cc9553e83bf1732fd7ba3d","tid":1243173,"uid":162558,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9aa846a4d3c5439d642d7c22234feff0299eceb","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4e262d0498dd80711cc9553e83bf1732fd7ba3d","tid":1243173,"uid":162558,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:00:55.000Z","msg":"隨便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44de963f2c293057d7dbe3c35f8719363d4449f8","tid":1243173,"uid":162558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9aa846a4d3c5439d642d7c22234feff0299eceb","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4e262d0498dd80711cc9553e83bf1732fd7ba3d","tid":1243173,"uid":162558,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:00:55.000Z","msg":"隨便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5cea75ea30668b863d4b7d5ec0d43b3fa7171e1","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"44de963f2c293057d7dbe3c35f8719363d4449f8","tid":1243173,"uid":162558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9aa846a4d3c5439d642d7c22234feff0299eceb","tid":1243173,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4e262d04